{"id": "352330", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=352330", "title": "Lorbu Sadsummon", "text": "Lorbu Sadsummon is a &lt;a href=\"gnome\"&gt;gnome&lt;/a&gt; found overlooking the &lt;a href=\"Wreck%20of%20Hellscream%27s%20Fist\"&gt;Wreck of Hellscream's Fist&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Jade%20Forest\"&gt;Jade Forest&lt;/a&gt;.\nNotes.\nLorbu is a warlock type with only two abilities: a straight-forward Shadow Bolt attack (3 sec cast) and the ability to summon a Succubus to fight for him. The Succubus deals melee damage, and uses her 'Enticing' ability to draw the player toward her. Lorbu has a respawn rate of only a few minutes.\nLorbu is notable for dropping &lt;a href=\"Cracked%20Talisman\"&gt;Cracked Talisman&lt;/a&gt;. This item has a 100% drop rate, and can be repeatedly acquired from Lorbu's corpse.\nLorbu's staff appears to be a purple version of &lt;a href=\"Terestian%27s%20Stranglestaff\"&gt;Terestian's Stranglestaff&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Medusoid%20Staff\"&gt;Medusoid Staff&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "427707", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=427707", "title": "Lorcan Flintedge", "text": "Lorcan Flintedge is a &lt;a href=\"dwarf\"&gt;dwarf&lt;/a&gt; located at the &lt;a href=\"Lunarfall\"&gt;Lunarfall&lt;/a&gt; in .\nHe can only be recruited using the Headhunter's Harvest from &lt;a href=\"Lunarfall%20Inn\"&gt;Lunarfall Inn&lt;/a&gt;.\nLorcan was present at the &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20Harbor\"&gt;Stormwind Harbor&lt;/a&gt; during the preparation for the Alliance assault on the &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Shore\"&gt;Broken Shore&lt;/a&gt;. He was on &lt;a href=\"Captain%20Angelica\"&gt;Captain Angelica&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"battleship\"&gt;battleship&lt;/a&gt;, awaiting for the departure and offering a sip of his private stash to other &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;s. The liquid was very strong and drinking it would instantly make someone drunk. A relief bucket was near him for those needing to... purge the alcohol out of their body.\nHe afterwards participated in the &lt;a href=\"Battle%20for%20the%20Broken%20Shore\"&gt;Battle for the Broken Shore&lt;/a&gt;. Considering he's one of the looks availables for the &lt;a href=\"Weary-Eyed%20Mourner\"&gt;Weary-Eyed Mourner&lt;/a&gt;s it seems he survived the defeat of the Alliance.\nQuotes.\nAye, another mission where we might not be makin' it back.\nBrought me private stash this time, though. Ye want a sip?"}
