{"id": "180892", "revid": "49723770", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=180892", "title": "Lord Afrasastrasz", "text": "Lord Afrasastrasz is a &lt;a href=\"red%20dragon\"&gt;red dragon&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; guise located at the &lt;a href=\"Wyrmrest%20Temple\"&gt;Wyrmrest Temple&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Dragonblight\"&gt;Dragonblight&lt;/a&gt;, where he serves as its highest military leader. He led the defenses against the &lt;a href=\"blue%20dragonflight\"&gt;blue dragonflight&lt;/a&gt; assault and later against &lt;a href=\"Deathwing\"&gt;Deathwing&lt;/a&gt;'s forces. He is an outspoken supporter of Alexstrasza.\nHe was also present at the meeting in the Wyrmrest Temple before and after the death of Deathwing. He seemed to sympathize with &lt;a href=\"Kalecgos\"&gt;Kalecgos&lt;/a&gt; wishing to keep the Wyrmrest Accord united, but did not speak up when the other &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Aspects\"&gt;Dragon Aspects&lt;/a&gt; proposed disbanding the organization.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Power%20of%20the%20Aspects\"&gt;Power of the Aspects&lt;/a&gt; buff can be disabled by talking to Lord Afrasastrasz at the beginning of Dragon Soul if a raid wishes to attempt the encounters without the aid of the Dragon Aspects.\nQuotes.\nWyrmrest Temple.\nQueen Alexstrasza has placed me in charge of the defense of Wyrmrest Temple.\nAs you know, &lt;a href=\"Malygos\"&gt;Malygos&lt;/a&gt; had his forces destroy a nearby ley line anchor. The forces of the dragonflight then redirected that power to the Azure Dragonshrine.\nThe blue dragons are using that power to strengthen themselves; so much so that they dare attack the temple itself! They're starting to win.\nAre you here to help us, &lt;race&gt;?\nDragon Soul.\nWe need to move quickly! Tyrygosa and her guard have fallen, leaving the temple defenseless. Deathwing's forces must never reach the Dragon Soul or all is lost. The Wyrmrest Accord will aid you in the assault; the siege must be broken!"}
