{"id": "740889", "revid": "46586549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=740889", "title": "Valdrakken Accord", "text": "The Valdrakken Accord is a &lt;a href=\"dragonkin\"&gt;draconic&lt;/a&gt; organization led by the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Aspects\"&gt;Dragon Aspects&lt;/a&gt; to represent the reunification of the dragonkin upon their home of the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Isles\"&gt;Dragon Isles&lt;/a&gt;. A spiritual successor to the &lt;a href=\"Wyrmrest%20Accord\"&gt;Wyrmrest Accord&lt;/a&gt;, the Valdrakken Accord takes its name from the mighty draconic city of &lt;a href=\"Valdrakken\"&gt;Valdrakken&lt;/a&gt;, upon which at the &lt;a href=\"Seat%20of%20the%20Aspects\"&gt;Seat of the Aspects&lt;/a&gt; the Dragon Aspects lead their people. Unlike the Wyrmrest Accord, the Valdrakken Accord contains representatives of all five flights, and is led by the five Dragon Aspects, &lt;a href=\"Alexstrasza\"&gt;Alexstrasza&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Nozdormu\"&gt;Nozdormu&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Kalecgos\"&gt;Kalecgos&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Merithra\"&gt;Merithra&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Ebyssian\"&gt;Ebyssian&lt;/a&gt;; the latter of whom was appointed by the accord themselves at the behest of his brothers, &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Sabellian\"&gt;Sabellian&lt;/a&gt;.\nQuests.\nQuestlines with the Valdrakken Accord are unlocked at various renown levels and are part of the &lt;a href=\"Friend%20of%20the%20Dragon%20Isles\"&gt;Friend of the Dragon Isles&lt;/a&gt; achievement: \nReputation.\nAs with most reputations in , the Valdrakken Accord uses the &lt;a href=\"Renown\"&gt;Renown&lt;/a&gt; system rather than traditional reputation gain. Most quests in the zone of &lt;a href=\"Thaldraszus\"&gt;Thaldraszus&lt;/a&gt; give reputation. Unlike the other reputations, Valdrakken Accord goes up to 30, rather than 25, renown due to the fact that it is the 'central' reputation of the expansion; granting reputation from many avenues outside of Thaldraszus as well.\nDescription.\n\"Centered in their most ancient city, the Valdrakken Accord is the unified might of all dragonkind, seeking to protect not only their island home but all of Azeroth.\"\nRewards.\nAll Renown rewards and unlocks are account-wide with the exception of profession recipes, non-cosmetic armor, and questlines (all marked with *s). "}
