{"id": "670296", "revid": "40741520", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=670296", "title": "Vale of Eternal Twilight", "text": "The Vale of Eternal Twilight is a constructed &lt;a href=\"plane\"&gt;realm&lt;/a&gt; created by &lt;a href=\"N%27Zoth\"&gt;N'Zoth&lt;/a&gt; as a corrupted form of the &lt;a href=\"Vale%20of%20Eternal%20Blossoms\"&gt;Vale of Eternal Blossoms&lt;/a&gt;. In this vision, the &lt;a href=\"Horde\"&gt;Horde&lt;/a&gt; forces at the &lt;a href=\"Shrine%20of%20Two%20Moons\"&gt;Shrine of Two Moons&lt;/a&gt; have fallen completely to the whispers of N'Zoth. Now an army of mindless thralls, they attacked the &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; forces at the &lt;a href=\"Shrine%20of%20Seven%20Stars\"&gt;Shrine of Seven Stars&lt;/a&gt;. With even those at the Alliance shrine beginning to fall to madness, those who remain sane ended up in a battle on two fronts. \nGo to the &lt;a href=\"Blacktalon%20Agent\"&gt;Blacktalon Agent&lt;/a&gt; in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms to get in."}
