{"id": "188581", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=188581", "title": "Valley of Ancient Winters", "text": "The Valley of Ancient Winters is located in the central reaches of the &lt;a href=\"Storm%20Peaks\"&gt;Storm Peaks&lt;/a&gt;, connecting &lt;a href=\"Brunnhildar%20Village\"&gt;Brunnhildar Village&lt;/a&gt; to the east, with &lt;a href=\"Dun%20Niffelem\"&gt;Dun Niffelem&lt;/a&gt; to the west. It is the site of a war between the Brunnhildar &lt;a href=\"Hyldnir\"&gt;Hyldnir&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Sons%20of%20Hodir\"&gt;Sons of Hodir&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt is inhabited by &lt;a href=\"frost%20giant\"&gt;frost giant&lt;/a&gt;s and their &lt;a href=\"frostworg\"&gt;frostworg&lt;/a&gt;s, the former of which is being attacked by bear riders from &lt;a href=\"Brunnhildar%20Village\"&gt;Brunnhildar Village&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Hibernal%20Cavern\"&gt;Hibernal Cavern&lt;/a&gt; is on the northern wall of the valley.\nPhasing.\nInitially, Hyldnir on war bears roam the area, attacking (and being attacked by) the frost giants and their frostworgs.\nAfter the character completes &lt;a href=\"The%20Drakkensryd\"&gt;The Drakkensryd&lt;/a&gt; quest (part of the &lt;a href=\"The%20Sons%20of%20Hodir%20quest%20chain\"&gt;Sons of Hodir quest chain&lt;/a&gt;), the Hyldnir retreat back to Brunnhildar Village, leaving the valley to the frost giants, the frostworgs, the mammoths, and the &lt;a href=\"Jormungar\"&gt;Jormungar&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "333452", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=333452", "title": "Valley of Ashes", "text": "The Valley of Ashes is an area in the &lt;a href=\"Burning%20Steppes\"&gt;Burning Steppes&lt;/a&gt;. It is a smoldering stretch of valley curving between the hills, with molten flows to the south and a charred plain to the north. Nothing but tough local wildlife lives here; the only sentient creatures in the area are the &lt;a href=\"black%20dragonflight\"&gt;black dragonflight&lt;/a&gt;. The valley is surrounded by inhospitable land, as &lt;a href=\"Dreadmaul%20Rock\"&gt;Dreadmaul Rock&lt;/a&gt; lies to the northeast, the &lt;a href=\"Ruins%20of%20Thaurissan\"&gt;Ruins of Thaurissan&lt;/a&gt; is to the northwest, and the &lt;a href=\"Blackrock%20clan\"&gt;Blackrock clan&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"Black%20Tooth%20Hovel\"&gt;Black Tooth Hovel&lt;/a&gt; is west. \nThe road running south through the valley leads through &lt;a href=\"Blackrock%20Pass\"&gt;Blackrock Pass&lt;/a&gt; and eventually into the &lt;a href=\"Redridge%20Mountains\"&gt;Redridge Mountains&lt;/a&gt;."}
