{"id": "470787", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=470787", "title": "Alliance (film universe)", "text": "The Alliance was created when the nations of the &lt;a href=\"Seven%20Kingdoms%20%28film%20universe%29\"&gt;seven human kingdoms&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Azeroth%20%28film%20universe%29\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt;, along with the &lt;a href=\"Dwarf\"&gt;dwarves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"High%20elf\"&gt;elves&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"gnome\"&gt;gnome&lt;/a&gt;s, joined together to fight against the &lt;a href=\"Horde%20%28film%20universe%29\"&gt;Horde&lt;/a&gt; after the death of &lt;a href=\"Llane%20Wrynn%20%28film%20universe%29\"&gt;King Llane&lt;/a&gt;.\nNations of the Alliance.\nFrom the meetings in Stormwind, every nation had 3 representatives. There were 24 people, with 3 elven and 3 dwarven ambassadors. This means one human nation was not present (either Dalaran or Alterac)."}
