%20Covenant\"&gt;emissary&lt;/a&gt; that Lord &lt;a href=\"Garithos\"&gt;Garithos&lt;/a&gt; sent to Prince &lt;a href=\"Kael%27thas%20Sunstrider\"&gt;Kael'thas Sunstrider&lt;/a&gt;."}
