{"id": "64503", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=64503", "title": "Alliance Forces", "text": "The Alliance Forces was an &lt;a href=\"organization\"&gt;organization&lt;/a&gt; that encompassed the &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"dwarf\"&gt;dwarves&lt;/a&gt; members of &lt;a href=\"Alliance%20of%20Lordaeron\"&gt;Alliance of Lordaeron&lt;/a&gt;. Shortly before the &lt;a href=\"Third%20War\"&gt;Third War&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"captain%20%28rank%29\"&gt;captain&lt;/a&gt; warned the &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt;s that they were violating the &lt;a href=\"Alliance%20Internment%20Act%E2%80%8E\"&gt;Alliance Internment Act\u200e&lt;/a&gt; and that they had captured an orc leader, &lt;a href=\"Grom%20Hellscream\"&gt;Grom Hellscream&lt;/a&gt;. Led by &lt;a href=\"Thrall\"&gt;Thrall&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Horde\"&gt;Orcish Horde&lt;/a&gt; attacked the &lt;a href=\"Southshore\"&gt;Alliance Naval Base&lt;/a&gt;, freed the orcs and Grom, and stole their ships and left &lt;a href=\"Lordaeron\"&gt;Lordaeron&lt;/a&gt;. Its &lt;a href=\"team%20color\"&gt;team color&lt;/a&gt; is blue."}
