{"id": "323148", "revid": "38791128", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=323148", "title": "Alliance organizations", "text": "This article is a list of Alliance organizations. Organizations within the &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Alliance%20of%20Lordaeron\"&gt;Alliance of Lordaeron&lt;/a&gt; and within its member states in &lt;a href=\"Azeroth\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Outland\"&gt;Outland&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Draenor%20%28alternate%20universe%29\"&gt;alternate Draenor&lt;/a&gt;.\nMembers.\nHigh King of the Alliance: &lt;a href=\"Anduin%20Wrynn\"&gt;Anduin Wrynn&lt;/a&gt;\nLord Commander of the Alliance Forces: &lt;a href=\"Turalyon\"&gt;Turalyon&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20%28kingdom%29\"&gt;Kingdom of Stormwind&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"King%20Anduin%20Wrynn\"&gt;King Anduin Wrynn&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Turalyon\"&gt;Regent Turalyon&lt;/a&gt; (in absentia)\nFormer leader(s): &lt;a href=\"King%20Varian%20Wrynn\"&gt;King Varian Wrynn&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Bolvar%20Fordragon\"&gt;Regent-Lord Bolvar Fordragon&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Anduin%20Lothar\"&gt;Regent-Lord Anduin Lothar&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Ironforge%20%28kingdom%29\"&gt;Kingdom of Ironforge&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Council%20of%20Three%20Hammers\"&gt;Council of Three Hammers&lt;/a&gt; - Members: \nFormer leader(s): &lt;a href=\"King%20Magni%20Bronzebeard\"&gt;King Magni Bronzebeard&lt;/a&gt;\n \n&lt;a href=\"Darnassus%20%28nation%29\"&gt;Nation of Darnassus&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"High%20Priestess%20Tyrande%20Whisperwind\"&gt;High Priestess Tyrande Whisperwind&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Malfurion%20Stormrage\"&gt;Archdruid Malfurion Stormrage&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Gnomeregan%20%28nation%29\"&gt;Nation of Gnomeregan&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"High%20Tinker%20Gelbin%20Mekkatorque\"&gt;High Tinker Gelbin Mekkatorque&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Exodar%20%28faction%29\"&gt;Exodar Draenei&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Prophet%20Velen\"&gt;Prophet Velen&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Gilneas%20%28kingdom%29\"&gt;Kingdom of Giilneas&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"King%20Genn%20Greymane\"&gt;King Genn Greymane&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Tushui%20Pandaren\"&gt;Tushui Pandaren&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Aysa%20Cloudsinger\"&gt;Master Aysa Cloudsinger&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Telogrus%20Rift\"&gt;Telogrus Rift Void elf&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Alleria%20Windrunner\"&gt;Alleria Windrunner&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Magister%20Umbric\"&gt;Magister Umbric&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Army%20of%20the%20Light\"&gt;Grand Army of the Light&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"High%20Exarch%20Turalyon\"&gt;High Exarch Turalyon&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Council%20of%20Exarchs%20%28Army%20of%20the%20Light%29\"&gt;Council of Exarchs&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Iron%20clan\"&gt;Dark Iron Nation&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Moira%20Thaurissan\"&gt;Queen-Regent Moira Thaurissan&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Kul%20Tiras%20%28kingdom%29\"&gt;Admiralty of Kul Tiras&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Jaina%20Proudmoore\"&gt;Lord Admiral Jaina Proudmoore&lt;/a&gt;\nFormer leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Katherine%20Proudmoore\"&gt;Lord Admiral Katherine Proudmoore&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Daelin%20Proudmoore\"&gt;Lord Admiral Daelin Proudmoore&lt;/a&gt;\n \n&lt;a href=\"Mechagon%20Island\"&gt;Kingdom of Mechagon&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"King%20Gelbin%20Mekkatorque\"&gt;King Gelbin Mekkatorque&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Prince%20Erazmin\"&gt;Prince Erazmin&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Obsidian%20Warders\"&gt;Obsidian Warders&lt;/a&gt;.\nCurrent leader(s): &lt;a href=\"Scalecommander%20Azurathel\"&gt;Scalecommander Azurathel&lt;/a&gt;\nHistorical factions and splinter groups.\n&lt;a href=\"Alliance%20of%20Lordaeron\"&gt;Alliance of Lordaeron&lt;/a&gt;.\nLast leader: &lt;a href=\"Terenas%20Menethil%20II\"&gt;Terenas Menethil II&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Human%20Expedition\"&gt;Human Expedition&lt;/a&gt;.\nLast leader: &lt;a href=\"Jaina%20Proudmoore\"&gt;Jaina Proudmoore&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"Alliance%20resistance\"&gt;Alliance resistance&lt;/a&gt;.\nLast leader: &lt;a href=\"Othmar%20Garithos\"&gt;Othmar Garithos&lt;/a&gt;"}
