&gt; inside:\nTaran Zhu's followup quest, &lt;a href=\"Secrets%20in%20the%20Isle%20of%20Thunder\"&gt;Secrets in the Isle of Thunder&lt;/a&gt;, is not part of the main progression, but it is something to do while otherwise questing."}
