{"id": "403344", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=403344", "title": "Arekk", "text": "Arekk is a &lt;a href=\"draenei\"&gt;draenei&lt;/a&gt; located at the &lt;a href=\"Bloodthorn%20Cave\"&gt;Bloodthorn Cave&lt;/a&gt; in . Along with his friends &lt;a href=\"Roona\"&gt;Roona&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Jorril\"&gt;Jorril&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Diaani\"&gt;Diaani&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Zuulo\"&gt;Zuulo&lt;/a&gt;, he went to &lt;a href=\"Bloodthorn%20Hill\"&gt;Bloodthorn Hill&lt;/a&gt; to collect the bounty on &lt;a href=\"Kliaa\"&gt;Kliaa&lt;/a&gt;. Unfortunately, he ate some of the mushrooms and fell asleep. With no way of fighting back, he was dragged all the way inside the cave by the &lt;a href=\"pale\"&gt;pale&lt;/a&gt; and is now trapped inside the cave. He would be freed by an &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "235105", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=235105", "title": "Arelas Brightstar", "text": "Arelas Brightstar is a &lt;a href=\"high%20elf\"&gt;high elf&lt;/a&gt; found in the center of &lt;a href=\"Crusaders%27%20Coliseum\"&gt;Crusaders' Coliseum&lt;/a&gt;. He acts as the herald for the various encounters, representing the &lt;a href=\"Silver%20Covenant\"&gt;Silver Covenant&lt;/a&gt;. He also spawns in the &lt;a href=\"Eventide\"&gt;Eventide&lt;/a&gt; District of Dalaran, atop a &lt;a href=\"%3ASilver%20Covenant%20Hippogryph\"&gt;:Silver Covenant Hippogryph&lt;/a&gt;, to invite players to the Argent Tournament.\nHe starts the events in &lt;a href=\"Trial%20of%20the%20Champion\"&gt;Trial of the Champion&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; players, but is killed and raised as a &lt;a href=\"ghoul\"&gt;ghoul&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=\"the%20Black%20Knight\"&gt;the Black Knight&lt;/a&gt; at the end of the &lt;a href=\"instance\"&gt;instance&lt;/a&gt;.\nHis &lt;a href=\"Horde\"&gt;Horde&lt;/a&gt; equivalent is &lt;a href=\"Jaeren%20Sunsworn\"&gt;Jaeren Sunsworn&lt;/a&gt;.\nQuotes.\nTrial of the Champion.\nGrand Champions.\nThe first challenge requires you to be mounted on an &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Warhorse%20%28NPC%29\"&gt;Argent Warhorses&lt;/a&gt;. You will find these mounts along the walls of this coliseum.\nPlease, mount the warhorse, speak to me, and then we can proceed.\nAre you ready for you first challenge, &lt;class&gt;?\n\"\"&lt;br&gt;\n\"Returning:\"&lt;br&gt;\nOR\nArgent Champion.\nThat was an impressive display. But are your ready for your next challenge?\nRelatives.\nHe may be related to &lt;a href=\"Balandar%20Brightstar\"&gt;Balandar Brightstar&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Caydori%20Brightstar\"&gt;Caydori Brightstar&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Kalaena%20Brightstar\"&gt;Kalaena Brightstar&lt;/a&gt;."}
