ia the repeatable side quest &lt;a href=\"Life%27s%20Finer%20Pleasures\"&gt;Life's Finer Pleasures&lt;/a&gt;).\nAs soon as the side quest is completed, she starts walking out of the town.\nUse the scroll on her, giving her the Carinda's Retribution buff."}
