{"id": "39293", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=39293", "title": "Argent Crusader", "text": "Argent Crusader is a caster staff with &lt;a href=\"stamina\"&gt;stamina&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"intellect\"&gt;intellect&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"spirit\"&gt;spirit&lt;/a&gt;.\nSource.\nArgent Crusader is a quest reward from the quest &lt;a href=\"The%20Argent%20Hold\"&gt;The Argent Hold&lt;/a&gt; which starts with &lt;a href=\"Lord%20Maxwell%20Tyrosus\"&gt;Lord Maxwell Tyrosus&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Light%27s%20Hope%20Chapel\"&gt;Light's Hope Chapel&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Eastern%20Plaguelands\"&gt;Eastern Plaguelands&lt;/a&gt;. The quest chain to get this weapon begins with &lt;a href=\"The%20Archivist\"&gt;The Archivist&lt;/a&gt; and then continues when you acquire the head of Balnazzar and accept the quest &lt;a href=\"The%20Truth%20Comes%20Crashing%20Down\"&gt;The Truth Comes Crashing Down&lt;/a&gt;."}
