{"id": "233176", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=233176", "title": "Argent Crusader's Tabard", "text": "Argent Crusader's Tabard can be purchased from &lt;a href=\"Evniki%20Kapsalis\"&gt;Dame Evniki Kapsalis&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Tournament%20Grounds\"&gt;Argent Tournament Grounds&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Icecrown\"&gt;Icecrown&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Northrend\"&gt;Northrend&lt;/a&gt; for . This can only be acquired by players who have attained the rank of , requiring &lt;a href=\"Exalted\"&gt;Exalted&lt;/a&gt; reputation with all your faction's core races and the &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Crusade\"&gt;Argent Crusade&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis item must be equipped to be used, and players who activates its effect will be &lt;a href=\"teleport\"&gt;teleport&lt;/a&gt;ed to the &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Pavilion\"&gt;Argent Pavilion&lt;/a&gt; in the Argent Tournament Grounds.\nIts cooldown is separate from that of the &lt;a href=\"Hearthstone\"&gt;Hearthstone&lt;/a&gt; and most other teleport items."}
